OL,5, Too many divorce cases are going to    
OL,6, court and the language used there is   
OL,7, too hostile, a leading judge has said. 
OL,9,FSir Andrew McFarlane - who is head of  
OL,10,Ffamily courts in England and Wales -   
OL,11,Festimated one fifth of marriage        
OL,12,Fbreak-ups were wrongly ending up in    
OL,13,Fcourt with one partner suing the other.
OL,15,FHe said parents are fooling themselves 
OL,16,Fif they think children are unaffected. 
OL,18,FIt is a rare public intervention from a
OL,19,Fsitting judge and his remarks are      
OL,20,Flikely to resonate with many families. 
